ck drone. Deals d6+TEC damage.",color:"#00FFD0"},"DRONE_Ladybug":{type:"DRONE",cost:"1E",stat:"TEC",desc:"Cyberdefense drone. Blocks one incoming hack.",color:"#FF6EC7"},"DRONE_OwO":{type:"DRONE",cost:"4E",stat:"TEC",desc:"Legendary drone. Unknown capabilities. Handle carefully.",color:"#FFD166"},"Health Pack":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Restore 4 HP.",color:"#00FFD0"},"Energy Cell":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Restore 4 Energy.",color:"#aaaaff"},"Starship Parts":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Repair 2 Hull on your starship.",color:"#888888"},"Stratogen Hormones":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Gain +1 to all stats for 3 turns.",color:"#FF6EC7"},"Contraband Package":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Valuable smuggled goods. Worth 50 Scraps at a Settlement.",color:"#FFD166"},"Data Shard":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Encrypted data fragment. Used in netrunner missions.",color:"#88BBFF"},"Flash Round":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Blinds target for 1 turn. Ranged use only.",color:"#FFD166"},"EMP Grenade":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Inflicts Shock on all enemies in range.",color:"#aaaaff"},"Taser Shell":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Inflicts Stun on hit. Weapon mod compatible.",color:"#FFD166"},"PowerGen":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Restore 6 Energy immediately.",color:"#aaaaff"},"ShieldStim":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Gain 2 Armor for 3 turns.",color:"#00FFD0"},"AntiVirus":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Remove all Hack status effects immediately.",color:"#FF6EC7"},"NGHTMR Key":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Access key for NGHTMR secure network nodes.",color:"#FF2060"},"NetLink":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Temporary network bridge. Reduces clock cost by 1.",color:"#88BBFF"},"CryptoSerum":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Digital currency extract. Worth 25-100 Scraps.",color:"#FFD166"},"Narcobiotic":{type:"ITEM",desc:"Combat stimulant. Gain +2 VIG and +2 GRA for 2 turns.",color:"#FF6B35"}};
